      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Given the cancellation, your best bet is to immediately check flight tracking apps for available options from other UK airports, as these might have more open seats than Heathrow right now. If you must stick to a single hub search, compare estimated total travel times for direct flights from London to Singapore versus connections through Doha (Qatar Airways) or Dubai (Emirates). Generally, a well-timed direct flight, even from a different city, will beat a multi-stop route when time is the critical factor. Contacting the airlines directly for rebooking options is also crucial, as they might have priority access to alternative routes.",
