    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so frustrating. i've been standing here for an hour and every time i think i have a plan, something else goes wrong. it feels like there's some kind of hidden force sabotaging everything, like the whole system is just designed to be unpredictable and difficult. is there any reason why airports get so incredibly messy during these kinds of mass disruptions?",
